td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: AoE and faction</span><hr size=1> i'd just pull and make sure you hit all mobs you agro at least once. you can tank them while the casters ae. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ucelestin.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Celestin</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(1/31/02 12:49:50 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3976.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: AoE and faction</span><hr size=1> Depends on the AE if you get faction (in Droga, other zones different) or not.<br><br>AE debuffs - no faction hit.<br>AE stuns or damage - faction hit.<br><br>I'd AE slow then cast my level 1 DD on everything and most of the time I could get the faction hits before stuff was dead.  Most of the times.  AE is the best way to do this quest.  PL-ing monks is a close second, but AE really cuts down on the time.<br><br>Celestin<br>Oracle of Bertoxx <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showMessage?topicID=3939.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showMessage?topicID=3330.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3976.topic&index=6><img src=http://www.thesafehouse.org/images/reply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.emailToFriend?topicID=3976.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email